{"tid":210631,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好，我係走數狗","createTime":"2017-04-21T05:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T17:42:35.000Z","uid":30768,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd332dba85faafa86277b7ea62fe1682567bc18","tid":210631,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]milk老師歷史有4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可否講講意大利統一</blockquote><br />\nYes等你教埋我世史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢又逃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果milk敢quote呢句認自己係走數狗，我請晒全個post既手足食譚+請milk食一個月</blockquote><br />\n我認我係走數狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件詳情係依個PO<br />\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/127327/page/4?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/127327/page/4?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我出完水之後話會貼真飛，好對唔住，我唔應該走數唔貼真飛。希望各位能夠原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望N賓找數請我食一個月譚仔同請波台手足食譚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794287b0ac512531b2da389b7c75aac95af8197c","tid":210631,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"lm等食tam"},{"pid":"5e168bb9e5b9adb519ac8c21fd454bdcb12a6b8e","tid":210631,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"1772c401b33a799ad75393fbbc5481f60efcb95a","tid":210631,"uid":38189